description:
This market will resolve to “Yes” if all of the following conditions are met at the HLTV awards:

- ZywOo is named top player of the year
- Vitality wins team of the year
- ZywOo wins awper of the year
- apEX wins igl of the year
- XTQZZZ wins coach of the year
- ropz wins closer of the year
- mezii wins anchor of the year

Otherwise, this market will resolve to “No”.

If, for any reason, one of these categories has not declared a winner by January 31, 2026, 11:59 PM ET, this market will resolve to "No".

It will suffice if the listed player is declared a co-winner in their respective category.

This market will remain open until it is confirmed that at least one of the above conditions has not been met, or until all of the above conditions have been met.

The primary resolution source will be official information from HLTV (https://www.hltv.org). A consensus of credible reporting may also be used.
